WEBVTT

00:08:59.830 --> 00:09:02.689
who appears totally cool and indifferent,

00:09:02.689 --> 00:09:05.838
while he has actually anticipated and calculated

00:09:05.838 --> 00:09:09.443
so that all eyes are on him.

00:09:09.443 --> 00:09:11.012
I think that becoming aware

00:09:11.012 --> 00:09:13.219
of this general imposture

00:09:13.219 --> 00:09:14.627
that concerns all of us

00:09:14.627 --> 00:09:16.447
would ease our love relationships.

00:09:16.447 --> 00:09:18.837
It is because I want to be loved

00:09:18.837 --> 00:09:20.334
from head to toe,

00:09:20.334 --> 00:09:22.309
justified in my every choice,

00:09:22.309 --> 00:09:25.081
that the seduction hysteria exists.

00:09:25.081 --> 00:09:27.374
And therefore I want to seem perfect

00:09:27.374 --> 00:09:28.994
so that another can love me.

00:09:28.994 --> 00:09:30.521
I want them to be perfect